  "prompt": "How do I know if a shy guy likes me?",
  "response": "Here are some signs a shy guy might like you:\n\n1. Body Language Signs\n- Frequent glances/eye contact\n- Nervousness around you\n- Positioning himself near you\n- Fidgeting or blushing when you talk\n\n2. Communication Signs\n- Tries to start conversations\n- Asks questions about you\n- Remembers small details you've mentioned\n- Responds to your messages quickly\n- Follows/likes your social media posts\n\n3. Behavioral Indicators\n- Seems more quiet or awkward around you\n- Wants to help you with things\n- Finds excuses to spend time with you\n- Gets jealous when you talk to other guys\n- Friends hint that he likes you\n\n4. Subtle Interactions\n- Tries to make you laugh\n- Mirrors your body language\n- Compliments you (even if subtly)\n- Seems genuinely interested in your life\n\n5. Deeper Signs\n- Shares personal information\n- Tries to connect on a deeper level\n- Shows vulnerability\n- Displays genuine care and concern\n\nRemember, every person is different, and these are general indicators. Direct communication is always the best way to understand someone's feelings.",
